                    <span>A truly excellent resource! This book is full of valuable exercises for challenging the irrational thoughts and avoidance behaviors that fuel social anxiety. I particularly appreciated the creative examples of how one can confront and overcome social and performance fears in a gradual and manageable fashion. Of all of the resources that I've come across to date, this book has been the most helpful to me in terms of offering realistic and practical strategies!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A great help!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
